## âœ¨ Features

- ğŸ” **Prefix-based city search** with debounced input
- âš¡ Instant in-memory search across 200k+ cities using optimized indexing
- ğŸ“ **Open city in Google Maps** with one tap
- ğŸ¨ Clean modern UI using **Jetpack Compose**
